# od-pdp: NestJS + Hexagonal + Event-Driven

## Folder layout
- `src/domain/**` — Pure domain logic. Ports (`*.port.ts`), services, types, errors. No Nest, no IO.
- `src/driving/**` — Inbound: Nest HTTP (`driving/nest/http/`), SQS consumers (`driving/nest/sqs/`), DTOs.
- `src/driven/**` — Outbound: Drizzle (`driven/drizzle/`), HTTP clients (`driven/http/`), EventBridge (`driven/eventbridge/`).
- `src/adapters/datadog/**` — Cross-cutting tracing/telemetry.
- `src/component-tests/**` — Higher-level tests (MSW, test-launcher, real DB).
- `src/test-utils/**`, `src/shared/**` — Fixtures, builders, utilities.

## Tech stack
- NestJS 11, Fastify, Vitest, Drizzle ORM, SQS, EventBridge, MSW.

## Path aliases
- `@domain/*`, `@driving/*`, `@driven/*`, `@shared/*`, `@test-utils/*`.
